      The key engineering challenge was making DQS reliable from such messy
      natural-language logs. Logs include mixed objective/subjective units (<code
        >tbsp</code
      >, <code>handful</code>, etc) and descriptive adjectives (<code
        >large</code
      >, <code>semi-skimmed</code>, etc).
    </p>

